  "excerpt": "How much phone do you need?",
  "image": "",
  "readTime": "1 min",
  "content": [
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How much phone do you need?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because it’s likely that you don’t need 8 gigs of ram or 256 gb of space any more than you need to spend a thousand dollars or half that on a phone.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How much car is required?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because getting from point A to point B isn’t the same as getting there in style (or on a full tank of gas).",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How much house is needed?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because being able to afford the ‘finer things in life’ is probably more satisfying (and important) than a few hundred or thousand more square feet.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How much media is urgent?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because more than enough isn’t the same as enough to get by.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How much education is necessary?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because bankrupting yourself on a 4 year degree isn’t always the ‘only best option’ to getting an education or building an asset.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How much impact is worth it?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because catering to the smallest viable audience is often just as if not more risky/meaningful/significant as mass production.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Asking yourself ‘how much is enough?’ is a reliable way to save for more of what’s essential and spend less (time, money and attention) on what isn’t.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}